                                        Structure
                                                                               <<05-02-26>>
->structure is a use difined data type which is contain similar and dis-similar data type eliments
->structure which is on kide of group which contain dis-similar data type eliments

Array    vs    structure

(1) Array
->array can contain only similar data eliment in single variable
(2) structure
-> structure can contain multiple  eliments of different data type in a single variable

Syntex:

struct<structure name>
{
    data type variadble name1;
    data type variadble name2;
    data type variadble name3;
    .....
};
